00:29:46.810 --> 00:29:46.850
<b>Vile Criminal</b>

426
00:29:53.100 --> 00:29:54.770
Who's that?

427
00:29:54.770 --> 00:29:59.900
This useless trash failed the mission assigned
to him by the shogun a the Flower Capital.

428
00:29:59.900 --> 00:30:04.910
Lord Orochi said to punish him
however we see fit!

429
00:30:10.170 --> 00:30:13.250
We present Kamazo the Reaper!

430
00:30:13.250 --> 00:30:17.580
So, you're that Kamazo I've heard
so much about, huh?!

431
00:30:17.580 --> 00:30:19.420
And there's one more!

432
00:30:27.350 --> 00:30:29.290
Stop right there.

433
00:30:29.290 --> 00:30:30.580
Here is my report:

434
00:30:30.580 --> 00:30:35.690
While we were escorting Kamazo here,
we caught another criminal!

435
00:30:36.380 --> 00:30:39.320
The escapee, Captain Kid!

436
00:30:39.760 --> 00:30:40.860
Jaggy!

437
00:30:41.280 --> 00:30:45.630
This scum was shouting something
as he approached us,

438
00:30:45.630 --> 00:30:48.660
so I put a few rounds in him.

439
00:30:48.660 --> 00:30:51.540
Even then, he didn't try to run!

440
00:30:51.540 --> 00:30:55.820
I guess he forgot he's wearing seastone cuffs!

441
00:30:56.750 --> 00:31:00.880
Kid! What, is your head full of rocks?!

442
00:31:10.260 --> 00:31:14.930
He got away clean, so why
did he get himself caught?!

443
00:31:21.310 --> 00:31:22.610
Hey, stop!

444
00:31:25.030 --> 00:31:26.900
I said stop!

445
00:31:29.130 --> 00:31:34.870
You used to say you hate
the way you laugh...

446
00:31:35.360 --> 00:31:39.820
At some point, you even quit
laughing out loud entirely!

447
00:31:39.820 --> 00:31:45.800
Weren't you the guy who beat anyone half
to death who mocked the way you laughed?!

448
00:31:49.280 --> 00:31:52.670
So just... stop it already...

449
00:31:52.670 --> 00:31:57.060
And then, you began to wear
a mask to hide your face...

450
00:31:57.660 --> 00:31:59.210
That's the person I knew...

451
00:32:00.350 --> 00:32:02.310
What the hell happened to you?!

452
00:32:02.780 --> 00:32:06.050
After we got separated,
what did Kaido do to you?!

453
00:32:06.050 --> 00:32:09.950
Or was it Orochi who got to you?!
Where's everyone else?!

454
00:32:11.410 --> 00:32:12.780
Answer me!

455
00:32:15.630 --> 00:32:17.460
C'mon, answer me...!

456
00:32:17.460 --> 00:32:18.910
Please answer me,

457
00:32:19.290 --> 00:32:21.110
Killer!

458
00:32:24.250 --> 00:32:26.300
What?! That's him?!

459
00:32:32.560 --> 00:32:35.770
That's the masked guy who was with Jaggy?

460
00:32:35.770 --> 00:32:39.120
Jaggy must've tried to save him...

461
00:32:39.120 --> 00:32:40.930
How cruel...

462
00:32:40.940 --> 00:32:43.160
Forced to eat a smile fruit,

463
00:32:43.160 --> 00:32:48.550
he's been stuck with a mask of laughter
he can never remove.

464
00:32:48.550 --> 00:32:51.320
That bastard Orochi does unspeakable things...

465
00:32:59.460 --> 00:33:02.830
What did they do to you
to change you so much?!

466
00:33:11.340 --> 00:33:16.350
Who did this to my partner?!

467
00:33:17.140 --> 00:33:20.560
Where is my crew?!

468
00:33:20.560 --> 00:33:23.440
Dammit!

469
00:33:44.290 --> 00:33:47.210
Don't screw with me!

470
00:33:48.670 --> 00:33:50.170
Damn you!

471
00:33:51.750 --> 00:33:54.450
You got something to say to me?

472
00:33:58.180 --> 00:34:03.190
That's right. I thought up a fun game.

473
00:34:18.870 --> 00:34:22.790
Sorry to keep you waiting,
you sons of bitches!

474
00:34:25.660 --> 00:34:28.130
The Sumo Inferno...

475
00:34:31.050 --> 00:34:33.680
is back on!

476
00:34:40.430 --> 00:34:44.690
However, there's a new rule.

477
00:34:44.690 --> 00:34:51.650
The blades in your collars kill you
the moment you step out of this ring.

478
00:34:52.420 --> 00:34:55.240
That rule hasn't changed.

479
00:34:55.240 --> 00:34:58.880
But the new rule is...

480
00:34:58.880 --> 00:35:05.120
as long as you guys are alive,
those two will be submerged in the water.

481
00:35:06.250 --> 00:35:10.650
In other words, as soon as
you and the geezer...

482
00:35:11.280 --> 00:35:12.920
are dead as door nails...

483
00:35:13.370 --> 00:35:15.950
we'll pull those two out of the water.

484
00:35:15.950 --> 00:35:19.640
That's just dumb!
I've got nothing to do with them!

485
00:35:19.640 --> 00:35:21.310
Oh, I know.

486
00:35:21.310 --> 00:35:23.620
But I do wonder,

487
00:35:23.620 --> 00:35:26.520
why has this rule made you upset?

488
00:35:28.150 --> 00:35:32.280
Is it because you two are rivals
from the same generation?

489
00:35:32.280 --> 00:35:37.030
If that's the case, then just sacrifice
yourself for them right away.

490
00:35:37.030 --> 00:35:40.790
Notoriety and bounties worth hundreds
of millions of berries mean squat...

491
00:35:40.790 --> 00:35:43.840
when all humans...

492
00:35:43.840 --> 00:35:48.980
drown in just five centimeters of water.

493
00:35:54.580 --> 00:35:57.760
Let the game begin!

494
00:36:33.580 --> 00:36:35.370
If that's how it is...

495
00:36:35.370 --> 00:36:38.220
join me in the ring!

496
00:36:39.680 --> 00:36:44.060
I'll kick your ass and end this!

497
00:36:54.180 --> 00:36:56.940
Who do you think you're talking to?

498
00:36:56.940 --> 00:36:59.950
Don't get cocky...

499
00:36:59.950 --> 00:37:02.030
you little punk!

500
00:37:06.200 --> 00:37:07.620
Sir Straw Hat!

501
00:37:14.340 --> 00:37:15.340
Hey.

502
00:37:17.920 --> 00:37:19.220
Punk.

503
00:37:22.840 --> 00:37:26.720
What possesses you to cling
to hope the way you do?

504
00:37:31.470 --> 00:37:36.150
Do you really think you'll
make it out of here alive?

505
00:37:37.030 --> 00:37:40.200
You think you can beat us?

506
00:37:43.450 --> 00:37:48.000
You are all going to die!

507
00:37:49.290 --> 00:37:51.710
One by one!

508
00:37:53.130 --> 00:37:55.880
Shut the hell up!

509
00:38:21.950 --> 00:38:24.030
I die...

510
00:38:25.500 --> 00:38:27.300
where I choose!

511
00:38:52.010 --> 00:38:54.560
Hey, what's that sound?!

512
00:38:58.980 --> 00:39:00.940
Hey, what's wrong?!

513
00:39:00.940 --> 00:39:02.400
Hey! Come in already!

514
00:39:03.360 --> 00:39:07.160
Queen, Your Awesomeness,
we lost contact with the gate guards!

515
00:39:42.610 --> 00:39:45.200
I finally made it.

516
00:39:49.410 --> 00:39:51.990
Oshiruko!
